[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說開覺自性般若波羅蜜多",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經卷第二",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856b24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚卿光梵",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856b26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大師賜紫沙門臣惟淨等奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856b27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856b28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人於色中所有不實分別分量及疑動分量，而能如實平等觀者，即於色中色而無所得；若於色中色無所得時，即於色中色見無所得；若於色中色見無所得，即於色中眾生無所得；若於色中眾生無所得，即於色中一切無所得；若於色中一切無所得時，即一切有所得。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856b28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若或於法有所得相可成立者，即有所得相而有依止。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故於彼大乘法中不能出離，何況聲聞、緣覺乘中。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人於受、想、行、識中所有不實分別分量及疑動分量，而能如實平等觀者，即識中識而無所得；若識中識無所得時，即識中識見無所得；若識中識見無所得，即識中眾生無所得；若識中眾生無所得，即識中一切無所得；若識中一切無所得時，即一切有所得。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若或於法有所得相可成立者，即有所得相而有依止，是故於彼大乘法中不能出離，何況聲聞、緣覺乘中。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩於諸色中，隨其言說即生取著、作用而行，如是行者，是行有身見，亦復行於有愛。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若或離有尋求而有所行，是於色中不了知相。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩於諸識中，隨其言說即生取著、作用而行，如是行者，是行有身見，亦復行於有愛。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若或離有尋求而有所行，是於識中不了知相。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩於諸色中，隨其言說不生取著、不作用而行。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是不行有身見，亦復不行有愛。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "離有尋求亦無所行，是於色中善了知相。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩於諸識中，隨其言說不生取著、不作用而行，是不行有身見，亦復不行有愛。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0856c29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "離有尋求亦無所行，是於識中善了知相。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於諸色中，能具三種心種子緣而攝受者，是為淨法。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、信解心種子，二、厭離心種子，三、不壞心種子。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於諸識中，能具三種心種子緣而攝受者，是為淨法。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、信解心種子，二、厭離心種子，三、不壞心種子。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於諸色中，應當發起三種之心。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、無取著心，二、無和合心，三、清淨心。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，須菩提，菩薩摩訶薩於彼色中，若心有生、若心無生，大生、平等生，悉應如實平等觀察。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由能如是平等觀故，是菩薩速疾證得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於諸識中，應當發起三種之心。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、無取著心，二、無和合心，三、清淨心。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於彼識中，若心有生、若心無生，大生、平等生，悉應如實平等觀察。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由能如是平等觀故，是菩薩速疾證得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於諸色中見有見無者，當知是菩薩不實知解。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於諸識中見有見無者，當知是菩薩不實知解。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩起心欲住平等界中，彼心於色求解脫時，即於色中其心動轉，有動遍動。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由如是故，當知此菩薩難得解脫。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩起心欲住平等界中，彼心於識求解脫時，即於識中其心動轉，有動遍動。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由如是故，當知此菩薩難得解脫。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩起心欲住平等界中，彼心於色求解脫時，若於色中心無繫著、無不繫著，由如是故，當知此菩薩善得解脫。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩起心欲住平等界中，彼心於識求解脫時，若於識中心無繫著、無不繫著，由如是故，當知此菩薩善得解脫。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於諸色中解無相法，苦自止息、諸相寂靜。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚夫異生不能如實了知色故，即於色中而生取著，現轉覆蔽。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由彼於色生取著心、現覆蔽已，即於聲聞、緣覺乘中不能出離，何況大乘。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又由如是取著、覆蔽因故，長時在於地獄、畜生、餓鬼、人、天諸趣，受生死苦，輪轉無盡。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是；乃至眼、色、眼識，耳、聲、耳識，鼻、香、鼻識，舌、味、舌識，身、觸、身識，意、法、意識，亦悉無性、假性、實性。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是意識於三性轉，愚夫異生不能如實了知識故，於識等中而生取著，現轉覆蔽。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由彼於識生取著心、現覆蔽已，即於聲聞、緣覺乘中不能出離，何況大乘。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又由如是取著、覆蔽因故，長時在於地獄、畜生、餓鬼、人、天諸趣，受生死苦，輪轉無盡。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857b29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是色於三性中轉，若有智者如實了知，即於色中不生取著，亦不現轉，其心開明。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由彼於色不生取著、心開明已，即於大乘法中而能出離，何況聲聞、緣覺乘中。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又由如是不生取著、心開明故，不於長時在彼地獄、畜生、餓鬼、人、天諸趣，受生死苦中推求。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於色無所得時，色即一切，都無照發；色無照已，即於色法平等性中如實了知，是菩薩速疾證得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於諸識中推求，於識無所得時，識即一切，都無照發；識無照已，即於識法平等性中如實了知，是菩薩速疾證得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。」",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊重說頌曰：「推求無異法，　　物境無照心，　智了於法性，　　此即得菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若於色中善解無性法者，即於色中色修作具足，而於色界亦無所動，是菩薩速疾證得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若於識中善解無性法者，即於識中識修作具足，而於法界亦無所動，是菩薩速疾證得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。」",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊重說頌曰：「智善解無性，　　修作悉具足，　亦不動法界，　　即得一切智。",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0857c28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0260_002:0858a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
